<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Hard_and_soft_C&action=edit&section=11.php.html" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><span class="citation" id="CITEREFArnaud1945">Arnaud, Leonard E. (1945), "Teaching the Pronunciation of "C" and "G" and the Spanish Diphthongs", <i>The Modern Language Journal</i> <b>29</b> (1): 37–39, <a href="Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307/318102">10.2307/318102</a>, <a href="JSTOR" title="JSTOR">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.jstor.org/stable/318102">318102</a></span></li>
